               bb]);
bb aa partitions `product'
(%o4)   r2 : aa bb -> [all atoms = aa, all nonatoms = bb]
(%i5) r2 (8 * (a + b) * sin(x));
(%o5)    [all atoms = 8, all nonatoms = (b + a) sin(x)]
